text: Holly Marie Combs (born December 3, 1973 in San Diego, California) is an American actress. She is best known for working on the television series Charmed. Before Charmed, she work in the TV series Picket Fences. == Other websites == * Category:1973 births Category:Living people Combs, Holly Marie Category:Charmed Category:Actors from San Diego
